\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Could you give me your full name please?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Mrs - Louisa Watson.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Your present address?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Box Tree Cottage. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 Colne Engaine, Colchester, Essex.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 The year of your marriage was 1945?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And the year of your birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 1888, January.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 The birthplace?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Brighouse - Colne Engaine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you know how many years you lived in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No I don't because - look, you understand, I was only a little kiddie. And I was a little kiddie when we moved to that next house. So I can't - no, it's no good, I can't tell you. If I knew I could tell you but I can't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you think that when you moved to the next house that you were already attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, we - 'cos I - attended from Brick House. As far as I can remember. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you know how long it was until you moved again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, I don't. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You had quite a lot of moves did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Look, we had Brighouse, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 Nightingales}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 , Peveralls - well that's - Blackhouse really, but - 'course got a different name now. And then back to Hungry Hall, and then from Hungry Hall down to village here, because 
they had to go and get a house where they could for 'em because - you see the governor died - and out you come - go where you can.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You had ten brothers and sisters, six boys and four girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Born pretty close together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well there weren't much difference. 'Cos even last - me and my sister was only a year and nine months. As near as I can tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You were the youngest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, I'm the youngest of all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And a sister next to you and then the other boys and girls going up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was the eldest child a boy or a girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well - I'll tell you as far as I - as near as I can. I think - whether Emily was after Arthur - or Harry - then I think come Emily. Then come the boy - then come under boys again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Your father and mother were both born about 1840?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Where did your father come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I should say Pebmarsh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And he was a horseman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you know if he ever had any other job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Only horseman. And of course - and when he got old you understand, couldn't use the horses, he went on day work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did that mean a drop in money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, that do make - mean a drop in money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you know if your father was ever out of work?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 He always had something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Where did your mother come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I - I should say from Pebmarsh as far as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you know if she worked before her marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 After her marriage she was occupied with the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 And she had to work - very, very hard. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 She did have to work hard, and I've had to work hard to. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 But then I don't mind, ain't no worse off for it did I.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you know if your mother ever did any casual work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 She didn't go pea picking or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Oh - oh my word, she could not with all they little kids. But I did. After - after a while. Yes, I did. When I left school. And I'll tell you what happened. My sister used to live at this - White Colne school, so I went pea picki
ng with her, so one day to see to - when I picked as many as she did, she had picked a load and I'd picked a lod, and I had as many as she did and I was only thirteen. I can tell you that bit. I tell you I could pick 'em in - in then, you know, that time.
 But then, you understand, we shared the money then. Well that's only }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 fair}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you remember what you got?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, oh my no, I cannot, that's a thing impossible.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I don't suppose it was very much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, they didn't get much, a lot. But I can'
t - it's no good, I can't tell you. No. I Mean, I - I'd tell you if I - if I could and - if I knew, but I can't remember all that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you remember which place it was that you lived in for most of your childhood, what's the house you've got the most m
emories of, is there one particular home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well there's Brighouse, Nightingales and Peverells and - as I tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not one that stands out, they're all the same are they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They're all farm houses. Excepting the two cottages that I tell you 
we had two for - you know - because the family. There - at - near Countess Cross, that's where it was
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were all the farm cottages much the same size?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well look, there was no farm cottages, only }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 this}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  here one here. And you had a go a good mile to 
- to the place. Yes, all that, because and - and the chase from the Hungry Hall from the gate to the wood was just a quarter of a mile long. And you understand I left school before I - I went up there. Just left - well you might say, only - well, a few mo
nths.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Thirteen. Because you had - because - you never - didn't come in that - the fourteen }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 till}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  afterwards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you ever have any relations or lodger living with you in any of your homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh my word, certainly not. Had enough to with the - with the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you tell me, the washing was done at home and you said you didn't have a proper copper in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, we did not because that was done in a washing boiler. We used to have to u
se that at Hungry Hall, and there was a copper at Pebmarsh - oh, copper at Peverells, but not at Hungry Hall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 How did you do the washing at Hungry Hall?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In - in the boiler. You know, you could - they just have - washing boilers in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you make a fire underneath it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh certainly you did. And burnt wood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you always do the washing on one particular day of the week in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh I can't - I can't tell you. Because you understand when there's a lot - you had to wash - often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 More than once a week?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
You do - got - come washing day you had a rare lot of - things. You come get six shirts, men's shirts. You know, that's a lot. Besides the other washing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 How did you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12338890\charrsid14557479 ring}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  them out then, did you have a mangle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well - no, by hands. People didn't have mangles in those days. No. Not for -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was it just the girls that helped your mother with the washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did the boys ever do any helping with the washing and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No. You see, they'd got to - go out - you see, in those days you had to start work six o'clock in the morning. Well you had to get up - pretty early didn't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What about when the boys were still at school, did they do anything to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well I - you see, I was young then, I couldn't - I can't remember. That's right, I - it's no good, I can't - that's beyond me to - remember all that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Because you were the youngest, you wouldn't have known so much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, of course I wouldn't. Now you understand - the other ones could have - would have remembered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 The oldest children in the family know more or that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Of course they would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You said that the shoes were repaired by the cobbler in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, and there was a - used to be - the Post Office used to be on the green down here. And they used to mend shoes in there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were the shoes bought there also?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, had to go to shop for that. Got to - go to Halstead.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 He didn't sell shoes or make them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. Mend. Mend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What about the clothes, how did your mother provide clothes for the children?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well there used to be a - club - club down at the school, you know, you pay so much a week - or so much a month. Then, you see, you could take that, and shoe club too. You see, and that used to help.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You drew the money out did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 How often could you get the money,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh, I can't - I - I don't know. That's no good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When you got the money could you go and spend it wherever you liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 As far as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It wasn't tied to a particular shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Not as I know of. So much in a - so much in the shilling. Well then I - I - that's no good, I can't tell you. But another thing you see that weren't kept on very long after I went. That was soon dropped.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 The school gave it up did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I wonder why that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I don't know, I can't - I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did your mother do any sewing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Only for our - for our own. There was enough to do, more than care for mending as well, darning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 She sewed your clothed did she, didn't buy them ready made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well she might have bought - the same as the coats. And then we had to make 'em do. 'Cos see what one - what - what - if they was too - if they was not big enough for the others you see then they'd come down. That's how it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Could you afford special clothes for Sundays or did you just have the same clothes on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh we had Sunday clothes on. Yes. And we had a - when we got in - off they come. And dresses too.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Where were they put then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Upstairs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Put away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well - of course we - you see, we used to go to Sunday school, come home - or go to church as well, come home, have our dinner, and then you see Sunday school again quarter past two or half past two, then again church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Straight after Sunday school the church was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. We always used to - 'cos we used to march from that school right up the church. And the teachers come too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Marching with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well they had - you see, they taught us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Then did you come back for tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes. And then - we didn't go out no more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You didn't play out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not Sunday nights. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When you got home did you have to take the Sunday clothes off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, we did have to take it off - Sunday things off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They were specially looked after were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, they were. We didn't go about in rags. They was mended.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you ever remember any clothes being bought second hand or given to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Yes. Yes, there was, we used to go to a - a jumble sale. And then perhaps if there was anything there, same as a coat, well that would be bought and of course they weren't dear then in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were shoes got there too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well that I've got to leave.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You didn't remember that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you tell me if your father did any domestic work in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No. 'Cos you see, he - understand he had quite - quite enough because there was a big garden. And a
nother thing you see then that got dark at night didn't it when they left off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So he was working in his garden on the summer evenings was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 As long as ever he could, yes. And the boys used to help as far as they could. When they was big enough
. I tell you we was all bought up to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was very important was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What other things did your parents think were very important, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well - oh yes, we had to go and pick - stone picking. To earn - to ear
n some money to buy clothes with. And - and - acorns was another job, and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12338890\charrsid14557479 gleaning.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  See, we used to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12338890\charrsid14557479 glean.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
 Well then the flour - no, the - wheat would be - go to the miller, and then that would be ground into flour, then we should have the flour you see. Y
ou'd have to pay just for the - grinding. I think I - I think I'm right there. But I know the - the corn used to be - yes, it did, put into flour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you use any of it for feeding the hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, because we weren't allowed to use none of our hens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You couldn't keep hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No, we couldn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You couldn't keep pigs either could you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. We could - we - and not even - allowed to keep a pig. What - you know, come from the garden went over in the farm yard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Into their farm yard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Well it's better than burning of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What about a rabbit or something like that, could you keep that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No. No. Nothing at all, not - not of your own.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you have any pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes. Had a pussy cat. Look.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And you had a dog?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No. No. No dogs. Because there - I'll tell you what - there was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 
license}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  to pay for it wasn't there. Well we'd got no money then those days to do - spend - to - for the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 license}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  and not the money to buy food with. 'Cos you couldn't get enough scraps off the table for a dog and cat. That's a thing impossible. -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So dogs were too expensive then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They - they was - were to - keep.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you ever remember your father doing anything for you when you were a little girl, like putting you to bed or looking after you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No, I can't remember nothing of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You think perhaps he didn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well he could have done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But you don't remember it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, I do not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember if any older sisters or brothers did anything for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well the sister - a - I believe the sisters used to help. And of course see when they was old enough - they had to go out to service. They had to go out you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They went quite young didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They did, were so m
any, they had to go. 'Cos you see, that's - the - then they could earn a little money for - themselves couldn't they. Another thing there was - you see there was less to feed. There was two you see old enough to go out. Well, I mean to say, one after the 
other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did the boys all stay at home and work from home, they didn't go off to farms too far away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No. They were working on the farm. And then see 'course the elder ones you see they married, two of 'em married. Then of course they - you see, the
n they had families, and - and then see, one lived at - Maplestead and the other one lived at Pebmarsh for a time. And - until they moved, one - moved off Hamson. I can remember that bit. But the one what lived at - Maplestead - well - they lived there fo
r years. Yes. They did.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you ever remember if your father took you out anywhere when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I can't remember that. No, I cannot, it's no good, I can't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you have any memories of your father, anything he did that stands out in your mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I can't, it's no good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You had to do a lot of work didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes I did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was there anything that was your own particular job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Cleaning shoes and do - and - getting the wood for the mornings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Where did you get the wood from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well you see, that - in those days you understand they had a fence and they used to cut it off. Well then you see, that was brought home - by the - the - tumbril or anything like that on the farm. Or if they cut a fence off there w
as always - what they called - odd wood, you see, because what was the odd wood you see, that weren't cut up like the other, that - and the faggots you see, the faggots what was sold on the farm, you know, for other people, they was quite different.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 These were just bits that weren't put in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You see, because I tell you that was - that had to be done just so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you got those odd bits?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you have to pay for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was something they gave you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I should think so too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What did you do with the acorns you got?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well we had - we sold 'em. Well you see then I had the money. But you didn't get much a bushel though. I shouldn't think you did. You had to go - you had to go a few hours I can tell you before you - you know, got -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What did you carry them in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Bag. Well you see -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 A cloth bag?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh those bags - you see, they used to be - what they call sugar bags, you could get them. As long as you paid for 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You used to buy a lot of things in bags in those days didn't you, like flour?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
And sugar. And flour - do you see, you couldn't use those bags 'cos they was very - they's real sacks - a purpose for flour, and nothing else. Well you see it weren't - according to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 what
\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  put in there they wouldn't be fit to eat. Not the flour wouldn't. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 
'Cos the men who used to - where we had our flour from was from - Wakes Colne.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You also used to clean the shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was the whole family's shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No, I didn't do 'em all. That - that's too much. As - as the boys got bigger they had to do their own. Well - I mean -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember if there were any special jobs you had to do for the older children in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see there was washing to
 do, there was ironing, there was mending, when you could - when - I say we was big enough to do it. And doing me own mending as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you do cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Used to help.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You made bread did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes, I - oh yes. Yes, because you see we'd want a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were you doing things like that when you were still a child?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh when we was - no. Not -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was later on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, because see - you see - you understand, your hands wouldn't be big enough to work the bread. 'Cos you se
e, those days they was - in a trough you see. Then that had to be by the fire so long. To rise. Because see, if - if that went cold you see the bread would be heavy. That would be. 'Cos you could - in those days you could eat bread a week old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Some people say it was better older, do you think it was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well our bread was always all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you keep it for a week before you ate it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh no. No. Well you couldn't - no, you see, ah we couldn't, we - there weren't room to put it. You see, b
ecause you come in twelve - say twelve to fourteen loaves, well - there - you see there weren't a lot of room for that. And - not little - not little tiny loaves you know. Big loaves. Then of course it got so - you see, then we had to buy bread. Couldn't 
do it then. And to tell you the truth the oven wasn't - oven was too far gone. So - and they wouldn't repair it, so therefore we had to buy bread. And the baker used to live down the village.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember if it was much more expensive to buy bread in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Of course it was. Cost more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember if you saw yourself off to bed or if you were put to bed when you were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 As far as I can tell you I - I really can't tell you. It's no good, I can't - no, I'll - yes, I - as 
far as I know but it's no good, I - I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You don't remember anything about bedtimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 We had to go to bed early.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 There was a certain time you had to be in bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, there was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And they were particular about that were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Weren't they. I tell you we had to mind when we were spoken to. We did.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 If grown ups were talking could you join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What did you have to do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well keep quiet. Unless you'd got a book to read.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you remember any of the things you had at mealtimes, breakfast for example?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well as far as I can - remember you see we didn't have bread and butter and jam. We had to make bread and jam do. And there weren't much meat to have - to be had either. You had it once a week - well - you had to make that do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that on a Sunday or another day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you finish it all up on the Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see, boys - when the boys went to work - you see, they had to have it. Well you see you couldn't p
ack them off with bread and jam could you. Not all bread and jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So on a weekday would you have some hot food in the middle of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, because you see - being at school, and that was too far, well of course we should have it at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you take something with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well - we had to have - we took - had to take a dinner, we was - we had too far to go. You know, backwards and forwards. Another thing, we couldn't do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you took something to eat with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Would it be some bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Yes. Bread and jam as far as I can remember. Well you see, it's no good. As I say, you - you couldn't get this - you see there weren't the stuff you're getting - then as there is now. Same as tined food, well - all - you know, 
tinned stuff. Well you couldn't get it in those days. You - we used to have it from the garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you have quite a lot of vegetables in your garden?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. We did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you had plenty of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, we did. We did have.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was it enough for the family or did they have to get extra?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well, can't - I just - it's no good, I can't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But you remember having quite a lot of vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, we did. Yes we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That would be in the evening would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 The main meal of the day was the evening meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was all the family together then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was there enough space for you all to sit down with such a big family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see - we - we had to make it do. We had a tidy table, and we had to sit round there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You cold all sit down for a meal could you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I - yes, I think we could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you tell me a bit about how you were expected to behave at table when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. We had to behave and not speak. And - and keep quiet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Couldn't you talk at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No. No, not when - I tell you we had to be very quiet. That's just the same when - if - same as when mother went to Halstead, see she could walk that bit then, and we went - if I went with her
, went into a friend's house - well I wouldn't have to talk, you just sit on a stool, quiet.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 While she and her friend talked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, she would - did. And you weren't allowed to go outside nor about. I tell you we was brought up strict. And it's a
ll the better for you too. I know it is.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Supposing at the meal you wanted some more, could you ask for some more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well if there was it we could have it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And you could ask for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh - oh yes, you could do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You could speak in that sort of way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes. Yes, like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were they particular how you sat at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh they didn't - no, didn't tell us about that. Only - they tell you you had to stop there 'til - the meal was over.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You couldn't get down just when you'd finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you have to wait until everyone had finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's right. Then you could get up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did they ever have grace?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I don't remember so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember if you could have brought a book or a toy to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No. Another thing, we didn't have toys in those days. Because you see - taking it that - the money wouldn't go to it. We might - we might have an old rag doll.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Would that be home made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, that would be home made. Oh I can - I can make a rag doll. Don't you worry. And I can dress it too. Yes I can.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you make dolls clothes when you were a child?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You learnt that sort of thing later on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes, I did - I can make a dolls - you know. But not the - I can't k
nit so well. But I can use my needle. In a - for a lot of things. 'Cos I tell you what, there's a man come up here - what, under a month ago, well he wanted me to do his trousers. Turn the bottoms up. And he had the fly fronts, you know what they are, the
 
- the sips. Well - do you know - and I hadn't done a pair like that before. I take it off, put the buttons and an odd piece of - for the button holes. And I managed it. Yes I did. I didn't do it quite right but - not first you know, I done it, so I - so -
 that is difficult. So - I - he was quite pleased with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did your mother do hooked rugs and this sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you have any kinds of rugs on the floor when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well there was coal matting. And hearth - and a hearth rug - a hearth rug. And as the boys got bigger they used to do some. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember whether at the table you always sat in the same place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes, we had our - we had our - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you have your own special knife do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh I don't know. Oh I can't - it's no good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you ever remember - you said there was nothing out of tins, you don't remember any tinned meat or tinned fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. There wasn't. You couldn't get them in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You said there were lots of rabbits round about here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, there used to be a lot of rabbits round about but you weren't allowed to go and catch 'em, not if they knew it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But I suppose people did didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well some of 'em - some of 'em did. But I c
an tell you - that I catch one, same as I went after milk one morning, I had some distance to go - I had - I brought a rabbit back. I caught it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Just with your hands
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It ran into you did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I had to run after it. And I had it to
o. Now don't you worry, I could run those - in those days. I could. Well I - well that was at Lamarsh. You see, they wanted me to go in this 'ere - pig race. That was a lay pig you understand. And they wouldn't go in before I did go. You had to pay sixpen
ce. And they said that I should have it. And I did have it. I runned and caught it. I did, and I hold it up. And that day - well you see I couldn't - they wouldn't let me - wouldn't let me cure - keep a pig, I sold it for thirty bob.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What pig did you sell?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
The one I caught. A live pig. Yes. Yes, you see - look, that was - that was - let go in the ring, you know, the people stood round. Well - and then this pigs was - let go. Yes. I - that was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 How old were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not very old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Still at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I left school then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 A teenager?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, that's it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And you sold it for thirty shillings?;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes I did. And by George you had to move then. If you were going - if you were going to catch a pig.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you run races with your friends and that kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
We weren't allowed to play, go outside in the road to play. Until - there was some children across the road where we lived, well we used to go - a little while. But not a regular thing. 'Cos you see they had a large - very large family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Even larger than yours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well - I - I really can't tell you how many there were but - then - then you see they moved from that cottage - to Pebmarsh. Into a bigger - into a farmhouse.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You told me that you didn't remember ever being punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No I don't. I don't say what - only a slight - you know. But that's a - that }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 ain't}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  being punished. Being punished is a good hiding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You never had a good hiding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, I don't remember that. I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember anybody else having one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No I don't. 'Cos I tell you we had to mind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You didn't disobey?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You didn't - well if we did then of course - you know - what's expected.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But you didn't do that very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. Well you see we weren't allowed to do it. And that make a difference.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember anything like being sent to bed without any tea or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Nothing like that at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Your parents brought you up to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Tell you we all had to work when we was old enough to do it. So we cold do it. And washing up particular. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did the boys do that too or just the girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see I can't tell you because I tell you - I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But you had to do a lot of washing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes we did. Had to do a lot of - because you see the two - the last two was girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you work together on things, you did the pea picking together didn't you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well - no. No because you see she had to go out service. Then I was le
ft. See, because she left school before I did. Then she had to be packed off to service.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 She wasn't the girl you went pea picking with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No, I went with a married sister. Yes. 'Cos you see, I went over there, and slept over there. I - I didn'
t come back every night. 'Cos that's no good - that - that be a little bit too far for me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 How long did you stay there for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 A week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you tell me what sort of behaviour your parents expected from you towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well - we didn't -
 I tell you we had to - we did have to mind. We didn't have to answer back. And keep quiet you know - spoke - speak when you're spoken to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was your mother easy to talk to, could you sort of chat to her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh - oh she was all right. Yes, she was a good mother to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's - well he was - he wasn't so tender hearted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 She was tender hearted was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes she was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 If you were worried about something could you tell her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes, if we was worried - we could go to - we could tell her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And she'd advise you and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
But she - but you see you - you wouldn't - we - well - see we didn't get into - trouble, you know what I mean, no, so we didn't have no rows and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You didn't have rows?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Because you were so strictly brought up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Tell you we was strictly - we - we was strictly brought up I can tell you. But then that's all the better for you, as you grow up - get on. But you see - of course you don't like to see other children do it do you. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Can you remember what other things they thought were important in life, did they talk to you about right and wrong and that type of thing, or was it more by example?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see, we - see we went to school, you kno
w, Sunday school, we was taught there. And then I tell you another thing, you see, we had a - of course I never have it now, but what they call text, you had to take a Bible and find 'em and write 'em down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that at Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. That was Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you get little texts to take home with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I think we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that Church of England?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Yes. Down here. 'Cos I never did get another one, only school - that school. I never did go to only that school. That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you think that both your parents were an equal influence on you or was your father more than your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well they was both alike really as near as I can tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Just like an ordinary day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Just like an ordinary day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You told me you used to hang your stockings up at Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's right, and get a penny and an orange. Well I tell you they couldn't - they hadn't got the money to do it with -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They tried to give you something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And they had a treat at school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Oh - yes, we had treat at school. In the Christmas time, you see, we had - a - Christmas tree, then in the summertime we used to go up to - the park. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Who was living there then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Barterell - Mr Barterell was one. He used to give us a treat. He used - and see we used to have a tea and games. And away you go home again, you weren't up there very long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did he do anything else for the people in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not as I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you look forward to the treat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Of course we did. Yes, 'course you see we did look forward - and we was taken up in the - horse and wagons. That's how we used to have to go up. Well you see there weren't the cars those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You said you had a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 melodeon}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 Accordion}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 . Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you ever have a sing-song or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh - sometimes we used to sing Sundays nights of - hymns.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you have any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What - to - well I had - did have one or two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were they Sunday school prizes and that type of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well - there would - but one - once a year, you know, the prize. Of course you didn't win a prize well you 
didn't - you know, if you didn't have enough marks you didn't get nothing. 'Cos it }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 ain\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
 like to day you see, as a rule - they have a prize, you know, they generally - buy all of them - or used to - something. You know, in latter years I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember your mother or father reading, had they learnt to read at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, they couldn't read. No, they could not.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did your mother read at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes she could read. And - and write. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 She would have grown up long before compulsory education wouldn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh - should think so, well she's been dead forty years. Or just over forty years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did she ever read aloud to him and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Used - used to - read a paper. 'Cos you see there were only one paper a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Which one was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Halstead paper, what they call the Halstead Times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Is that still going?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see, it's still going, yes, about two or three - in the Standard. 'Cos you see - because you see that's into one now. But I prefe
r the Halstead paper - separate, because you see you would - there's more in it and all about the villages, you know, round about. That's right. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What about magazines, was there a parish magazine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. And I believe that had to be paid for. But I don't think it was much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did they ever read aloud to you children from the paper or anything, tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not - not out the papers, no. Well you see, tell you, there was only one paper. And you see they didn't read the books - 'til 
tell you we had to go to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was the paper used for the fire when it was read?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I should say so. Or for - well one paper }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 ain\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  - you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 ain\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  going to - do much with that are you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did she put it on the shelves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Everything was used then wasn't it, nothing was wasted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No, the - that wasn't wasted. Well you see you hadn't got the stuff, you couldn't get it - you couldn't get it. And we weren't allowed to spend money - same as they have ten bob or more than that a week n
ow to go to the - children do - go and spend. But the horsemen used to have ten bob a week. They did. And then - you understand, that's years ago. Of course then they got - bit more afterwards. And -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you sometimes get a penny pocket money or only at Christmas time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
We didn't have money to spend. I can tell you. You couldn't - that's no good, you could not do it. You could not, it's no good saying you could, 'cos you could not. 'Cos time you took the money away for food and all that, shoes an
d clothes all come out of that, well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 There wasn't anything much over for extras?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, there - no there wasn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did your mother ever make - puddings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I should think she did. We didn't - we didn't go without pudding don't you worry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you tell me some of the types of puddings she made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well as a rule Sundays a meat pudding and what they call a light pudding, suet pudding. They was both together. You know, you've had that. Piece of - suet pudding and piece of - meat pudding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you start with the pudding before the meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What about during the week, did you have a bit of pudding on weekdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I tell you I - really I can't - I can't remember all that, that's -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But you had them on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Sunday. And as for go down to seaside. Well we didn't - we couldn't did - we couldn't do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You didn't go out on any kind of Sunday school picnics or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, because there was none in those days. No, because they come afterwards you see, in later years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember if there was any temperance club at the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No. No. No. There used to be down here afterwards - what they call a Girls Friendly.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Could you tell me a bit about that, were you a member?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. 'Cos you see that didn't - that didn't start 'til afterwards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You were grown up then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 There weren't any things like }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 Women\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  Institutes then were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh my word - no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember if your mother ever went out to a meeting or to any kind of club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, I can't remember she going out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was she mostly in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 She was. I don't say but what - if she - could - she'd go to church sometimes. When we got bigger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When you were little I don't suppose she could?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well how can you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You cooked meat on the midday at Sunday didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were you in the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. 'Cos there only used to be - boys in a choir then. That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And men as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes. Yes. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember on Sundays did your parents think it was wrong to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well they didn't used to work - only what was just necessary.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you know if your father was interested in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you remember if you took an interest in politics before the first war?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No I - no I didn't take no interest. Only I'll tell you one thing - the second - world war, I went and helped in the - on the land. }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 Well a lot of the men was taken away - well - and the work - and they was very glad for the women to go to work, so there was two of us on the farm. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 One at the other farm and one - and where we lived. So we used to work together. So I could - you - either take start and do same as the mend did, I mean p
ut the stooks, same as the wheat or anything like that, put it and set it up in rows. I could do that right enough. But that was only -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Could you tell me a bit about docking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well, see, you go in the corn and there are these docks what they all 
want to see down. Well you see I go and pull them up by hand, and lay 'em in heaps. And weeding - was by a weeding book, going up same as thistle and all - anything like that, in the corn. You had to be - going up and down the land. And pea picking. No, b
e
fore you get to that. Harvest time, see there was two of us, we used to go and - put the shocks up. The sheaves into the - into the rows. And - after that - oh no, before that, but don't matter, that's early part, then when went - been pea picking, stone 
picking. Well - until the corn was high enough you mustn't go in - you know, couldn't go more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It would be bad for the corn?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you couldn't see. You couldn't see the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 How exactly did you do stone picking, did you put them in piles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In a - heaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 About how high was a heap?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well look, if a - if the - there was plenty of stones - you could put one load on a heap and perhaps a little bit more. That's when the stones was thick round. You see, then you didn't get to carry them far.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you didn't normally have to carry stones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not far. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You mean you'd bring them from a little way round to a central part?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's right. And - and then put them in the heap. While the corn was - so you could do it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you work with a group of other women?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No. Well you see there was two of us doing the harvest work, what lived on the farms. But otherwise I - I went alone. And of course pea picking you had to do with the women.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In a group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. You do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Tell me about the clover?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well - you see - what - I think that used to have to be done in October. The clover seed, that was cut by a little reaper. And there was what they called swarthes. You had to take a - like a linen prop and turn it ov
er 'til it had dried before they could cart it. That's how they used to do that. They used to lay all in rows.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You used to do that work yourself did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well, there was others had to help. I believe if I remember right the men had to help with 
it too. I - as far - well not - say there - I believe there - perhaps there was two of us went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But it was work that both men and women did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. I think men done some of it. And as I say that is - that is a long time ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was pea picking always woman's work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 Men\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  too. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 Children\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 . They used to take the little kids in the field about there o'clock in the morning, half past two. They did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What did the children do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well play about. And those big enough you understand, they had to help their mothers. But that was long days for 'em I can tell you.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you do that work when you were very little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. After I left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you start on that sort of work as soon as you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Soon after. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that your main job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh - well look - see I had to be at home to help with the housework, washing, all that, baking.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Is that why they didn't send you away to service?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see there must be one at home. So if I wasn't at home the other ones had to come home. That's how.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you have any idea how long you continued doing that work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Now I - now that you ask me - but some - some few years I did. Yes. And then there was gleaning. You see, we used to go out gleaning, soon after we l
eft school. Then bring the corn home - cut the ears off, then that had to go to the mill and then that be milled into flour. Then the flour would come and that would be - that be - we used to use it for baking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You used to bake your own bread from it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Of course we baked - we - baked bread, oh for years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But then your oven wasn't good enough at one time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was at - that was latter end. Another thing that wasn't safe. That wasn't safe to - to - bake any more, 'cos on account of t
he fire. And on account of the thatched - the thatch.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you were working in agricultural work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 For a number of years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you know if you were doing that during the first world war? Do you have any memories of the first war at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I went to school then. I was at school. So that was the second world war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What you've been telling me about now was during the second world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Yes.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did they call them land girls, is that what they used to call them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see a land girl is one who always work on the land, winter and summer. Milk cows or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But you weren't doing that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. OH no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You were still helping at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. That's right. 'Cos I went - I used to leave off - I didn't go - you know, just - do so long and then leave off. Well of course -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 A few months at a time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, no, the time in the daytime. Because you see -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 A few hours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, only a few hours a day because see - I tell you I had to do housework. And I was doing washing. So I couldn't be there all the time.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Up to being about thirty years old would you be doing that work too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well - getting on that way. Getting on that way. And then I'll tell you a
nother thing I used to do, that is what they call - of course you don't understand it, single mangold out. You see, there's rows of mangold and as they were sown you see they're a bit thick. Well then you'd have to go and pull all them out and leave one. 
About - say about that part - that - distance apart. And that was - that was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 back aching}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you work with sugar beet too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's a difficult job I believe?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That is - that's hard work. But not today because they have - t
hey do it quite different. Or potato picking - picking, I've done that. You see, things come back after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That must have been a backbreaking job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was - that was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you do that on - your own or did you sort of do it with a partner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No, I used to do it - there was a little farmer - say they want me to help, help pick the spuds up and I went. That was - only - see I only used to help them, I was alone Not alone, but I was with - one - the man's wife what worked, you know, on - farme
r's wife, I went to help her.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You used to work together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Would you be paid on an hourly rate for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh I - well I can't - I tell you this - I can't remember. I'll tell you all I can remember but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When you were in your teenage years and your twenties you weren't in service?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Oh I'll tell you what else I - you see, then I couldn't work on the land no more well then I went to a place to help - do washing. For - you know, for few hours. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 That\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  a - that was - once a fort
night I believe. Until they had - or unto - well, when they lived at the other farm, then they moved into a cottage, because you see - the - their daughter - their sister died with consumption, and then - Ralph married, well he lived in the other farm. Th
en the - all afterwards all the lot was - all the lot was - sold, and then - Ralph had one farm you understand, then the others - the two boys and their uncle lived in the cottage, well away - from - from the farm. 'Cos they was all grown up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But you didn't go to the cottage, you went to the farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I did - after - yes, but you understand, when those - when they - moved the cottage, see, I used to go and help do their washing. Yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was once a fortnight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I think it was once a fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 How many years did you go there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh - it's no good you ask, I can't tell you. I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was it quite a long time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 For some time I did, yes, but I really can't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you ever have a job like your sisters did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not like they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not living in somebody's house and doing the housework and washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
You see, I used to come - I used to go - just for - just few hours in the morning. I didn't do - I didn't go - no, no, I didn't go every day. 'Cos I couldn't do it. And
 do - do the - the work at home, I couldn't - I tell you I used to go - a little while, you know, in the daytime.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Your jobs were never ones where you were living away from home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I was away a few months, but not very long, but - but you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 ain\rquote 
t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  going to put that down. That's got to be cancelled. Not that bit, I mean to say you're not to go and put that bit in, not - I was away from home a few months but not long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So really your main work was in the fields, doing all the different things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's right. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was it mainly for the farmer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That your father was employed by?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Of course - yes, of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that the usual custom, that girls and women would work for the man's farmer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you se
e, when the - when the war was on they was glad of anybody. So two of us went. Who lived in the farm houses. One lived across the field. But that don't matter. But she used to come, same - you know same as we used to go together. For the - farm - for the 
- harvest time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you ever think you'd have liked to have done any other kind of work or didn't you think that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I didn't - it's no good thinking that, 'cos I knew - I knew what - you know, yes, I did. And another thing I - I couldn't g
o - I mean to say, as the others was out, and there was the boys, there was - boy - four at home, with father and mother and me there was six, so it's quite enough to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So it was your job really at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 While you were doing agricultural work did anyone ever ask you to join a trade union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No, because that wasn't in - that - that wasn't - about, no. No, that wasn't - not for some - long time after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When you were doing this work did you always work on Saturdays?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. I did not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Or Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Me? No. I wouldn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were some people working on that sort of work on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I don't know if they did or not, but I didn't. I had my - I done it the six - you know, during the week. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479 And another thing they didn't do a lot on Sundays, not - not with - because you see - some people wouldn't help a farmer, the farmers couldn't get a man to go. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. 'Cos another thing, you see, they want a little rest don't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can I ask you a little bit about school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I'll tell you as far as I know because I left when we was thirteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you know when you started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When I was five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember anything about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh - we had - very good teacher.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was there just the one teacher in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Oh yes, there was more than - because see - well I - I can't tell you much about Mr Broadbent, I know his name. Then you see there was a - schoolmaster come. And then of course there was a - classroom, one for the - for the ot
her children, smaller children. And then you see - the - then there was - well she's dead now. I can't think of the one's name. I can't think of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you get on quite well with the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Well I'll tell you what, once, and that was be
cause I went down to a girl's house and I was late for school, so that day when I got back I had six strokes of the cane. No, I did. Just because I was a few minutes late. Well it was my own fault. Yes, but - you see, they dare not do it now. But I always
 got on well at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was the only time you ever got the cane was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's - far as I can remember, but I've remembered that well enough. 'Cos that didn't half sting too. On the hands.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was the cane used quite a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, that}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16450370\charrsid14557479  was}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  used a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 For small things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well - different things - if you - see, if they caught you talking together or - sometimes - sometimes - like copy one down - off another one's - book. But that's the only time I really can remember having of it. I didn't - I didn't forget it either.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did your parents take an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well then you see, in those days they didn't take so much interest in what they do today. No. Because it was quite on a different scale altogether. 'C
os today you see the lessons at school is different again. Because see - when I went to school we had to do needlework. I believe we had it twice a week. And we had to make useful things. But today - they don't do much needlework. And the same as knitting
, well some - some had knitting and some had needlework. Same as socks or different - all different things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you remember any sort of cliques in the school or gangs of children that would get together and fight other children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No. Not in - not then. No, not then. 'Course they fight today don't they. Well I don't know about here but they do it at school.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were there any children who came from a work house or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Where was the nearest one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was
 - be at - that used to be at Halstead. But they don't call it the work house now. That's all finished with. And you see - and - it's - some people, you know, what's very poor, there was - there was so much bread or - about two loaves I believe, it was ab
out two loaves a week - extra. Well that was a job to live in those days. That was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did any of the people you knew have to get the bread from there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I really can't tell you who did have to have it 'cos you see, the people - they're dead.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Some people used to say they'd do anything rather than ask them because they didn't treat them very well?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well you see they didn't - used - I think there was one or two - and I'll tell you another thing, where anybody got three children at school they had three hundredweight of coal Christmas, but that been stopped a long time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that through the church or through the Board of Guardians?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It was through a gentleman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was it Mr }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 Cotterall}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Cotterall. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 This was for any person with three children at the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Or three - or - look - when the - and when, shall we say three young children, well they used to have it like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That went on for years didn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That did. Then that stopped.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What about a joint of beef or something, was that over given to people at Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well look - one place - I can only tell you one place - that was - they was allowed so much, and just because there was somebody - I think they didn't say thank you, tha
t was stopped. That was. Only the - well that was Mrs Grimston, but she used to think of the children - the husband's wives. You know, and give 'em - give 'em - give them something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In the way of foodstuffs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In - wearing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Ready made or material would it be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
I believe that was made. And I'll tell you another thing now. Of course that got broke off, the doctor for Earls Colne, he used to give - oh a quarter a pound of tea, and I think it was two pound of sugar at Christmas time. But that
 got - that got - done away with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that a long time ago?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was a long time ago. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You remember that when you were a young girl?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, I can remember it. Because you see, then - you had to pay so much a week or - for - if you 
paid so much a week you see you could have the doctor free.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did your family do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And he was an Earls Colne doctor was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That - yes, that was Earls Colne doctor. And then was paid - no, no, they was paid so much a quarter. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Sort of a club he organised?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did that cover medicines too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, that covered everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did your mother ever make any of her own medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Same as medicines or - oh, senna. Senna - you know what senna pods are. Brimstone was another thing. And - salts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you have that every week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I'm afraid - we had to have it when we - you know - really wanted it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But not regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you ever remember hearing of families who had it regularly every week of their lives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
I can't tell you. No, I can't. 'Cos I tell you what - you see - we didn't - didn't just go in - run in and out of other people's houses. No. Well I don't here. Although there's one next door, when - Grace come he
re she knock at the door. When - if I want anything and - I knock at her door. Same as when she go out if I want anything she'll bring it, so when I go out if she want anything I get it. That's how we go on, but we don't run in and out. You know, not -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were there some people who used to go in and out with out a knock or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not as far as I know, but we didn't.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you have any relations actually in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, I used to - my grandmother and father used to live down the vil
lage here. That's when they was getting on, getting - so they couldn't work, so they come to the cottage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Is that when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you go to them often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I went - 'cos Mr Arnfield - he used to be very good, he was a cler
gyman. And been over here when Mr Sills wife - first wife, well of course he didn't marry again, she was very good to the poor. Yes, she was, she was very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that a long time ago?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 Yes, well she's been dead - oh long, long time.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In Colne Engaine there wasn't a doctor actually living there was there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No, there was not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did they have a squire here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 There wasn't one family that was more important than any others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not that I know of. Only I'll tell you at Pebmarsh. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 
Earls Colne doctor used to have a room there once or twice a week, I believe it was twice a week if I remember right. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
And then of course they used to go there, well you see, that made a difference. Otherwise if you wanted him any - you know if you wanted him for anything - had to send for him. 'Cos there was no telephone - telephone about then so much. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 People would often go by foot to fetch the doctor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's - well you had to go by foot. 'Cos see, the people hadn't - they didn't have no bicycles. Well I - I never had a bicycle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you never have one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I did, after - yes, I did afterwards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were you grown up before you had one?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, and when I was a kiddie - I'd no - well you couldn't afford it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When you were a teenager and in your twenties, did you go for walks as recreation, something to do, was this a sort of pastime you did?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I tell you what - we was brought up strict and we weren't allowed out of a night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not even in the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not - tell you we wasn't allowed out. That }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 ain\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  like it is today. You see, the kids go out here and play, 'til late at night time. Another thing is the lights about now aren't they. There was no lights here, if you went anywhere you had to go in the dark.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But on summer evenings you didn't go for walks when you were young, it wasn't a thing your family did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No. No, tell you we - we didn't - you see we lived right out of the village. 'Course there was children across the road, but you see they didn't have to do as they like, and we didn't have to do as we like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Their mother and your mother had the same ideas did they about bringing up children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh she was - the only one - a good mother. And so was my mother a good mother. She was. 'Cos I
 can tell you - one thing I can remember is going across to - Countess House and getting some eggs. And that's where we had to go and get our drinking water. Because there used to be a light left in the scullery, you know, when it's dark winter nights, to
 get the water. To pump it up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was outside?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was inside. Just inside the scullery. And a sink.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You'd have to fetch it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Of course we did. Because there was no - there was only pumps about, there was no - not the water - the mains wasn't laid then.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you bring a bucket with you or something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well I - I used to take something. I can't - but I couldn't take much, not - you can't, not when you're young, you can't. And another thing - that was some little way down the road to Earls Colne Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you go every night to get water in the winter?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see we have - we went - when we wanted, see because - and we used to put it in a pot - a big pot. You know, purpose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that an earthenware pot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It keeps it cool doesn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Another thing you see - you couldn't keep it in pails. 'Cos it weren't fit. You know, I mean to say they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 ain\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  to fit to drink them pails. So if you keep it in a big pot - pot hold four - I say - fou
r pails of - four pails I should say, four. Well - then you see when that was getting down, off you'd go again. Go and get some more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did boys do that as well or was that just the girls job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh no, oh you see - I couldn't - you see, the - my brothers used to - have to go and - go and get some. Well you could see you can't -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It was something everybody had to do, all the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I can't tell you about other people's children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In your family you all took a turn at this sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh we - well we did have to do, yes, we did take turns.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you ever remember your mother making wine or beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, we - we - did used to make wine. And brew beer for harvest time. 'Cos you see that was cheaper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did your father club together with some other people to make that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No. No, make it on your own. Because you see then perhaps some people wouldn't agree. You see. You - if you have it on your own, you go to - you go and get a pint when you want it. 'Cos you see that was made in big - vessels.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Where did you keep them after you'd made it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In what they call a shed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not in the house itself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. Oh you couldn't - there weren't room enough.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You made quite a lot did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well - yes, did - yes, there was two, you know, two vessels.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you ever make wine out of anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, same as orange wine or - you know, fruit. That's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did she make jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. We used to go and pick the blackberries when we left - come home from school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 She made blackberry jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Yes, and - and different - of course different kinds of jam. Well you see there used to be more fruit trees in the garden then. Yes. And of course see today - well - 'cos look at the plum tree used to be across here, but there }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 ain\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  none today. I don't know what happened to the fruit trees.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You heard that somebody didn't get the beef because they didn't say thank you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were you brought up to show respect to certain people more than to others in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well you see in those days, don't matter who it was, ladies and gentlemen, you had to make a - make a curtsey to them and the lads had a - well - well do like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Touch the forelock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's it. And of course then that got broke off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Have you any idea when that got broke off, were you grown up and people were still doing that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Oh long - yes. If I remember right. But that soon got broke off. 'Cos you see then - those days you had to say, yes ma'am, no ma'am, yes sir, yes miss, all like that. But they don't do it today because they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 ain\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  - can't get the maids to do the work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you say that to people whom you were working for though? If you met the doctor or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes, of course you did. Well, I mean
 to say - if you knew how to behave well you would do it you see. And another thing, I'll tell you, well children in those days was different what they are today. Because you see - look at 'em today. Look - look how they answer you back, look how they swe
ar. There's a lot - oh, there's a great difference.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you not remember children swearing when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, fear I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You knew the words but you didn't say them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well, I hadn't better. No, still there is a great differen
ce in children being brought up today. 'Course some of - even - here three and four, they'll swear - oh they will swear terrible. They do down here don't they. Well they do down here. Yes they do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But you don't remember hearing the children swear when you were a schoolchild?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No I don't. No because I tell you that was - I daren't - I doubt if they did do it. Don't remember, they don't do it a second time I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was there a major landowner in the village, did somebody own most of the cottages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No. No, there was more you see, more gentry about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Who owned most of the cottages, the people at Colne Park?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see they had the - he had his own property. You know, the houses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But there wasn't a sort of squire in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh no, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did the parson have any property?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But there were quite a lot of families who were thought of as gentry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They was - well another thing was you see they'd got the money of course and they could - you know, they could - be boss and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Who would they be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Courtaulds and different ones. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Who was at Colne Park?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 Cotterall}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 . Di}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
