\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You had to go and get the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 soup}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
