\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 If you wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you ever get it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, I don't - I don't ever remember going up. And that was - years ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you ever remember the term a real gentleman or a real lady, did people talk like that about people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well there was a - quite a difference in the gentry in the days gone by. Yes, there was a - good - a good - big difference.
