\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well - they did think themselves so high. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 How did they behave towards people then? How did they treat the people then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well all right as far as I know but of course see I didn't - I - I can't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You didn't work for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you wouldn't be calling them ma'am and sir and all that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh you'd have to - yes you would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In the village you'd have to call them ma'am and all that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you know the ones what - was - high - much higher up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Everybody knew them did they, they all would know who they were and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well - but - yes. But today - you see today I don't know a quarter - not half a quarter. 'Cos see there's a lot of - see it's all those new houses, there's a new school - school built and look - and the
n look at that house the other way, look at - now they're a going to build some more down here. Where there used to be a farm, farm buildings.
\par 
