\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh my word. Yes. That have. Well you got Countess Cross, well you see, there was two new }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12338890\charrsid14557479 houses}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
 built one side, then there's - one - two - three, four, five - six - and one against the wood, there's a bungalow, that's all - they're all fresh built this last few years. 'Cos there didn't used to be a house at all along that r
oad. Oh then there's another just side - just the other side of the wood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 There wasn't really much village below the church and the school in the past was there
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. Well you see, then -
