\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, good job too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was the pond always there, by }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 Pudney's}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. It's always - yes, that been there for years and years. Ever since I was little - kid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did people ever used to skate on it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They did used to skate. That - well that was hard winters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And they had hot summers then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, that was - much - very hot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You weren't allowed to play out at night were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In the afternoons could you play after school when you were a little girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, we had - no. We had - we had our work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you ever remember people getting together with a lot of tin cans and making a noise outside people's houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That didn't happen in Colne Engaine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. I don't - no, I don't ever - I don't ever remember they doing that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was the policeman seen around much, was there a policeman in the village then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 There used to be one in station in Colne Engaine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did he walk round much, did everybody know him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see, yes, he had walk round, he had to go so far and meet another one at night. Certain time, you know, certain - time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And then they would go together would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Then they'd part you see. You see, they'd meet a certain, you know - this one -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Change over you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Then they had to go - go and do their duty. You know, go around.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 How did the police treat the people at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well as far as I know all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did your mother ever say, I'll call a policeman if you're naughty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 She didn't frighten you with that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You remember something about making lye?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you tell me about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Yes, well you see you have an old tin bath, and you bore a hole, knock a hole in the bottom. You put straw first, a little straw, not much. Then you get an old bag - then you put the ashes, not coal, you m
ust have coal ashes, you must have wood ashes. Then you put that on - the bag. Well then you put a little water at top - little water at a time, then that drain through. And then that's like - that's like soft water. But you mustn't have too strong. If yo
u do that's going to - that hurt your skin. You mustn't have it too strong because it do the - well it's like anything else, you might say like soda water, you know what I mean. But that's very clear and that's very good for washing. You'd be surprised.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 still need}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  soap to wash with though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh you must have soap.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But it made the soap last better?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well of course it do and you see - that's a - that's more like soft water. 'Cos }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 soft}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  water - you see you don't want so much soap.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 The water's very hard round here isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That is.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you do that regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No. When - you see, it rained and when you catch soft water, you see, you could use that. But more - more so in the - in the - summertime. Because see that did
n't freeze. See you can't have it in the wintertime especially if that freeze because - that water what you put on top of these ashes - well that - that couldn't get through. That freeze on the top and freeze underneath.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you did it more in the summertime?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you remember any other things that you used to do like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well do you know I - if I tell you the truth I began to think of things, and then of course this happened and that did make a difference. But I'll tell you as fa
r as - they things - some of 'em might come back. Yes. But there was different things - but did I tell you about - in a clover seeding time, you see a machine would go and cut - cut - cut the clover and then you had like a - well you know a linen prop is 
like, that - that go like that don't it. With a long handle. Well then we used to take that and turn what they call the swalls over to dry ready for carting. That's another job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You used to do that work yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I used to help. See, because then
 the men could come along and cart it. 'Cos clover seeds well that's - well you see you must have it dry. And that - 'cos that isn't cut 'til - end of September or the beginning of October the time. Oh another thing, did I tell you when we were short of w
a
ter - no - when the water was - when the pond was drying indoors - in - in the garden. Well we had to go what they call - what they call Blackbush lay - pond with two pails of water to fetch for washing. Until - they had a - what they call a butt, water b
utt, and bought, some water. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You had to get the water from the pond did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
That's - that's - you see, you had to go - oh, more than five minutes walk. To this pond in the field to bring the water back - for washing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that water quite clear?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was beautiful clear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You could use it just like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You didn't have to filter it or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh no, no, nothing of that. Nothing that kind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But later on there was a water butt was there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well then they used to bring a - bring the water. Well so they ought I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that a cart?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
A - see that was water cart, well that's a - well they used to call 'em water butts. Well that hold - oh - gallons and - I can't tell you how many but - gal
lons and gallons, because, when you see the - what they call the horse pond was dry - which was now and gain, they had to go and fetch water for the cattle. That's how. And that was a farm house that was. Then - you see, there was no water - no pump, unti
l long time afterwards then Mrs Grimston had a word with the owner of the farm, she had a pump, just outside, well say four yards from the back door. Then there was water there, you know, for - for use.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And you used to go and get it from there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Of course we did. Well instead of going right across the - across as I told you, White Colne. Well that is Whitel Colne district.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's a long way to have to go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And specially when that was so went. And then when - you see, when that rained a lo
t and the - there used to be what they call the land ditch, you see, the water used to go off the - the - you see they piped the land - the land was piped. Well then the water got into this 'ere pipes and that water was very good for - for cooking, washin
g or drinking, anything. 'Cos that - yes, providing that didn't too - too - rain too much. That really was very good. That was pure. And that's another thing we done.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you had quite a lot to do really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well there - well there was a lot, well I done it and done it 'til I couldn't do it no longer. I did. 'Cos I had such a pain in my back.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It really hurt your back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well if you come to get two -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You had it pulling on your arms hadn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. But we used to have a hoop - what
 they call - made - homemade one. Well then you put that on the pails, then you get in the - in the middle of it, then - you see, that balance the pails and that was much easier to bring.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You mean that was on your shoulders?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, that was on - lo
ok - say this was a pail and that's a pail. Well you'd have the hoop on the - where the handles are, then you'd hop into the - this 'ere, yes, and then take the pails like that, and - but what you meant for the - shoulders, they had what they call a yoke,
 with two chains and hook it on, but that weren't so well. That was easy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Better than a ho}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 p?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. That was, much better.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you go and fetch your milk too when you needed it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. I used to go - well - part the way by foot in Pebmars
h district. Well then, when they give up milk - give up - the cows, then I used to go - there was a field of wheat - say - there's a field of wheat, well I went right through that, made a foot path through the hedge, through another field - and then into 
the - field where the farm was. Right down there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Quite a way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was, but I still - you see, and I made a footpath. But there was never a word said about it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You told your mother used to take you to visit your aunt and you used to have to sit quiet and not talk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
That's - look - that's when we - mother used to go to Halstead and that was a friend. And then - we went in, we had to sit still. Not - and be - we had to speak when we were spoken to. And we weren't allowed to run about. 'C
os you see we was brought up strict, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So when she took you here you'd come indoors with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes, certainly. And - sit down. Not run about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Would she go there for tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh no, no, go to Halstead you see to - shopping. That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And then she'd just call in on this friend of hers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did she ever have a meal there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, not as I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did she have a cup of tea or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well look - I don't think so because you see - people in tho
se days they couldn't afford it because they - she was only a poor person. They couldn't afford it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You were saying that you weren't brought up to go in and out of neighbour's houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. We wasn't. And I don't do it now. Even next door. Same as
 when she come here, I knock at the door and then - she say, come in. But I don't walk in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was your mother the same in that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 She was 'til - another thing you see we lived in a farmhouse, just down here, that's where I was born, at Brighouse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 This friend your mother had in Halstead, was she a friend from here childhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 On the way from - you see, that was part of the way to Halstead. Not in Halstead. No, in - part of the way. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that a childhood friend of your mother's, had she known her many years?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I can't - well see I couldn't tell you. I really couldn't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Would she have any friends in the village that she would go and see sometimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. Of course she had quite enough to do - to - well of c
ourse she used to go to church at - sometimes and you see you had - those days there was no buses running. There was no conveyance, you had to - you had to walk to Halstead - and back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did she walk to Halstead then with you when she used to go there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
We used - yes, see - but of course she couldn't take us all, only - I think one at a time went, that's how. And of course the others was left home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you ever in the first thirty years of your life go away for a holiday anywhere?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 
Because I tell you, you couldn't - you hadn't - you hadn't got the money to - to - go away, another thing, people daren't have their holidays in those days as what they do now. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
And when they do - finish harvest they was allowed one day off. Only one day. That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What did people usually do with that day, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well tend to go to Sudbury or anywhere like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Somewhere a bit further off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And - and they has to go by train, well - it's no good, as I tell you, we - in those
 days, poor people they were bad off, no good saying they wasn't. 'Cos they hadn't - they hadn't got the money to spare only for what - you know, for - what you wanted most, same as - you know, and same as you couldn't - we never used to have a tin of - t
in of fruit or anything of that kind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No extras of that kind at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No. Not same as what you can get today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were all the poor people about the same or were some better off than others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They was all round about the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What about people in things like building work and carpenters, were they better off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well of course they had a little more money. But they're wages was very poor - in those days. They were poor too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember at school if some of the children s
eemed much better dressed than other. Well if there was only one in a family - they could be dressed better. 'Cos I tell you we have - well - you know you couldn't go to shop - and get all new things because there was too many, so one took - when those - 
when things weren't big enough for one you know, you - handed - that's right, that's the idea, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What were the shops in the village at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Only one. Only one little shop in this village. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 
And a Post Office with a letter box used to stand on Colne Engaine Green, you know, where that - where that pillar box is now. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
And that man, that - his name was Mr Fuller, well he used to mend shoes. Yes. But there's none in Colne Engaine, not a shop like that now. They was all pulled down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So to go to the shops people had to go to Halstead?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Yes. Or - to Earls Colne. And of course Earls Colne now is much bigger than that was then - then, those days. And if you wanted doctor, well according to what part you lived, you had a long way to go. And 
one day I remember 'cos I was a bit late he wouldn't attend to me. I had to go - go up in the next day. That's how. And you had to walk then. 'Cos there's no - you couldn't afford a bicycle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that Earls Colne you'd have to walk to see the doctor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And he wouldn't see you because you were a bit late?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well - one of 'em, there's one particular.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was he a bit hard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well he was. He hadn't got much feeling. And one time -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were there any that were good to the poorer people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well I was just going to tell you, one time in long time back, Christmas time you'd have perhaps probably a quarter pound of tea given you and I think it was two pound of sugar, but I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 ain't}
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  quite positive about that, but I know you had - tea. And that was only for the poorest of people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Yes, that's right. Well then you see - I think that was sixpence a quarter, you had - you paid for a doctor. Well then you see you could have the medicine free.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So that was a good thing, that was a sort of sick club?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was to pay for the doctor you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And if you didn't pay your sixpence?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh - well I think - I think that was sixpence a child I believe. Well - you see - if you didn't keep it up, we
ll there you are, you know what to expect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember when you were a child realizing your parents had a struggle, at that time did you realize it do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well - I did so far. And you see I - well - when you're very young you can't remember all. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You mean it's more when you get older you look back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
But - you can memory - you can remember more things as you get on, say ten or eleven. 'Cos we had rather a long way to go to school. And then - one farmhouse we lived, well w
e had to come right along the Pebmarsh Road and then turn across from Countess Cross down to this school and that was a long way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 How long did that take you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well - you can't do it under half hour. When that was fine we could go by the fields. I can remember that well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When it wasn't fine you had to go by the road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. 'Cos you couldn't - 'cos it was too muddy to go by the field.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What did you do then for midday dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Take us - take it with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Take some bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Bread - and jam. 'Cos see - people in those days used to make a lot of jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They used to gather the fruit did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, because you see there used to be fruit trees in the garden. More than what there is today. There used to be apple trees
. And one place there was nice pears. And greengage trees.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you made a lot of jam to have with the bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you had to.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you make jam out of carrots?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. Don't know about that. Well now you've got so far, have you heard of - tomato jam? Oh, that's very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you make that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, because we - we didn't grow tomatoes in those days. No, no tomatoes, not -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What about rhubarb jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh - well we did make rhubarb. There was rhubarb - about but - and you see you
 got to be careful how you make that, you know, you want different - you want ginger and - if you don't make that properly that's all like slop. Yes it is. But as for gooseberry jam, blackcurrant jam and fruit jam, you know, same as - plum, greengage, dam
son, you see, if you do it the right way, you can turn the pots upside down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you remember before you left school if you ever earned any money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Yes, 'cos we had to go to - go to - in the fields to stone pick at night when we'd left off - 
when we come from school, to earn a little money to help buy the things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you did stone picking from when you were quite a young child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Oh when we was big enough you know to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Would you be about ten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, about ten and eleven, somewhere about there. Yes, I can remember quite well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Any other things you did while you were still at school in the way of earning a bit of extra, did you do gleaning when you were a school child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. We did. Because look - we used to go and 
glean and get enough wheat - and then that used to go to the millers. Then they used to grind - grind it into flour. And then, you see, we used to have the flour. 'Cos they used to have the part - part of it you know, the - what come off the flour, you kn
ow, in - little kernels in. Well then there's all this 'ere - husks. Well, they accounted we - paid in - I think we must have a paid a little for - for -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Getting it done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Perhaps he kept some back did he?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well - well that I shall have to leave. 'Cos you know you want a lot of ears to make a half a sack of flour. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember anything about politics in the village at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Nothing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Perhaps your parents didn't talk about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, you see, they'd got something else to think about, you know what I mean to say. You see, they couldn't go out by night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You don't remember people coming and getting people to join a workers union or an agricultural union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No. No, and I don't think that was in those days. As far as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You didn't hear people talk about Joseph Archer's union or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did your father ever go out in the evening at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 He was always at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 He was at home. Unless that was - now and again of a Saturday night he'd have to go to Halstead, and get the shop - groceries. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 He'd do that while your mother stopped behind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's right. Because he - he had to go when he left of work. Because in those days you see they didn't have the half a }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 day\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  holiday, you know, the same as they do today. They had to work all the week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They would just have Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes, they had Sunday. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did he ever go to the pub?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Never?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I don't remember ever he going to a pub for a drink. Well I tell you there weren't the money to spare.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Some people went if they didn't have the money didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, well perhaps they got into debt about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But he didn't go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did women in the village go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you - I don't know. Because see we used to live quite out of the village, so of course I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When you came to live in the village later on do you remember women going to a pub at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well there's always sure to be some of them go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It wasn't considered the right thing for women to do though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Of course it wasn't. Of course you see - tell you they hadn't got the money to spare to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So it was considered a bit to be neglecting your family if you went was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I should think so too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you remember if there was any sport in the village, did people play any kind of sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I think there was cricket. As far as I can tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did your brothers or father play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you ever go and watch it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. 'Cos I tell you what, we weren't allowed - to run about the roads.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Even when you were grown up you didn't go and watch cricket?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were you not interested in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 W
ell another thing that was too far to go. That was. Another thing, I - you see, I could find something else to do. And another thing you see, that }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 isn\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  gotten so I could - if there was a - conveyance you see to go and come back, or if I got a bicycle to g
o and come back. 'Cos she - you couldn't - you couldn't afford a bicycle. And I'll tell you what, in those days - the stones what used to be picked off the land - well there'd be what they call a stone - a man who breaks stones, they're the roadmen. Well 
- those stones would be put in the road and they'd just be very rough-walking, because that }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 ain\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
 like today, the roller didn't go over 'em. And that was rough I can tell you. And you see, another thing, those days you see you couldn't - a bicycle, if you h
ad a bicycle, that - that got no - very hard tyres. Yes. Yes. 'Cos you see, you couldn't go - it was harder work - to ride a bicycle, because on account of these here tyres. Then of course one thing got to another, then they got}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14557479  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12338890\charrsid14557479 tyres}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  with wind - tubes in. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You got a bicycle when you got older thought didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I got a bicycle I think - when I was over twenty. Or I might have been just under twenty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When you got it did you use it for cycling round in the countryside?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Just to get to places?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Just to - used to go to Halstead or - to a place like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You didn't go out on cycle rides for pleasure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No. And another thing they won't have cycle rides, not for pleasure in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 People didn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What about going for walks for pleasure, did people do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well if we did we went on the - farm land.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not along the roads?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. Tell you we weren't allowed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Even when you were grown up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see - not - not at fourteen, not at - you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But were you allowed more freedom when you were in your twenties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Oh - oh yes, of course I - made a difference then. Because I'll tell you what I used to do, when I left school - just down the road - a woman had a baby
. Well - and she'd want me to go down and take - and - take it out. And do you know, that child got so that knew me and that knew when I spoke to it, you know, it didn't do as it like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you go there every day to see it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I can't say I went every day but I - but - yes, but I used to go and take it out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In a pram would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In a mail - what they call a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 mail cart}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  those days. This - that hold one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 How long did you do that for, quite a number of months?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh some time. B
ut I be - I tell you that's been so long ago - but that's so long ago I can't - I can't remember. And I can tell you another instance, and that's when I was across the house, when Mrs Silver's ill I had to get up about in the middle of the night, 'cos peo
ple hadn't got telephones, not - lot of 'em hadn't then. I had to go right down the old - what they call the old rectory, right across the - a - the clergyman used to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 live down}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  there, they had to go right down to church then, but then you see it - in time t
hat altered so they got a house in the village. Well I had to go down there to - take a message to - to - for the lady who lived there to phone over to the Pebmarsh, to the doctors. And when I got inside the - inside the drive there was an old dog there. 
L
ook, I went that way and the dog was there. I - I talked to the dog like I'm doing now and I knocked at the - well, rung the bell so she - I could - I woke her up and - that dog, that stood just far off front door what didn't interfere with me. But they h
a
d to call that indoors before I could leave the - house - front door. And - that was Mr Dunne lived down there then, that was his name, and he said what - pluck I'd got to go like that, that if that dog had interfered - if that had have bit me, well he wo
u
ld have been in a very bad way about it. It worried him. But I tell you I kept going and going 'til I did get to the house and I stood there - I went there and the dog was that way, I tell you that followed me all the way, and I hadn't got nothing in my h
and, and I wasn't dressed properly. Well you see there weren't much time to get dressed. And I went all alone.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you feel terribly frightened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see, when the old dog was like that that did make you feel a bit touchy, but still that don
't matter, I wouldn't give in. I kept on. 'Cos probably if I'd have turned around and come back, that old dog'd - you don't know, that might have bit me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What kind of a dog was it, do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I can't tell you the name of the dog but that was a rather big dog. But I never forgot that. I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that when you were living in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When I was living across here. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When did you go there, was that after the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well - well I should say - I should say I was twenty-eight or something like that. Some - as near as I can tell you. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you stay there until you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And then you left did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well no, I used to go backwards and for - back doing work here and go across there and - few 
morning - you know, and help 'cos she hadn't go nobody else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you kept on there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Yes, I did for a time. Then of course she got somebody. Then of course I didn't go so often then. But I used to go across in morning and get the fire going, for a
 time. And can tell you - yes, the same time. Well where - you see - when - when a farm is sold - when the governor die, well you - you're given a months notice to clear out, especially when other people want the farm. Well then the - we live where we - i
n
 front of where the Leather Bottle is on the green, up the top, near Countess Cross. You'll have to wait a minute 'til I can - oh I know. Well then you see one of my sisters - she had a cancer, she was - she was very ill. Well for three weeks - all but on
e
 night I think it was, well say three weeks as near enough, I used to go up there every other night to sit up with her, come back here in the morning, do my work here, go across there and - start there. And then - then I had to see the - had to come back 
and cook the dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You must have got very tired?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I was tired. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You did that for three whole weeks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, I - I think that's three weeks all but one - I think, one - one night. But the last night, when I got up there, my sister h
ad just passed away. And you see I used to have her up here, she used to come up here and stay with me for a time for a change. So as she couldn't - you see, she got too ill. So - then I used to be - go up - different time - well, and then bring the washi
ng some of it back. I don't say I done all the washing but I done - I done some of it. To give a hand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you stop working when you were sixty or sixty-five?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Before then. Well - you know - like I tell you I didn't work - I didn't go - Cross Hous
e so much after - after Mrs Silver got - got help - in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you go over occasionally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When they needed some extra work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And you see when this one lived in, well perhaps she had - she had two there for a time. But 
I used to go then - to do some of the work. To help. And - then of course when I was - got - getting on, well - I - that's }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 no good}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  I - you see, that was too much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So did you stop before you were pension age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No, I had my pension. I had the pension you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Before you stopped or after you stopped?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, I - look I used to go backwards and forwards but mind you I weren't in - I weren't full service. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Just part time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's it, yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You were there with her for many years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I was there some long time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember anybody that you knew having to get help like those loaves of bread?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well that - that - that is - that's what they call Parish Relief.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember anybody you knew having to do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I - I can't - I can't remember, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But nobody you knew personally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But I remember the - you know, they was allowed. Or, if their husband was ill - you see they'd be allowed - little then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You said your family had to struggle hard, did they ever have to get any help from outside?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. Only - only Christmas - well before Christmas, you know, there used to be a blanket - loan.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But that was more like a gift really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, ah but we didn't keep it.
 Had to wash it and go back to the rectory again. Oh no, you weren't allowed to keep that blanket. They was loaned - they was loaned out you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Loaned at Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well in then winter - in the winter - in the wintertime. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Then you had to give them back again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 Well I tell you, you had to wash 'em and send 'em back clean.}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you just kept them say from November to March?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh about those - about that - year end. And some of 'em was very poor. The blankets was. 'Co
s they - see they weren't renewed. That was - and then - you see, one time - Christmastime - you - where there are - one or two go to school, or a woman with three little children they was allowed three hundredweight of coal. That's what - that's what - w
hat they call the gift coal. But there's nothing of that kind now. And there haven't been for a long time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you remember whether at school the teachers were particular about the girls and boys being tidy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I - well look - they went to scho
ol tidy - and sometimes I tell you what they very - and - they got livestock in their heads. And the clean ones - with the - the girls with clean heads, well - they used to catch 'em. Cos I was one on 'em.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You caught it from one of the others, lice were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Yes, they was. You see they'd been big ones, and then there'd be what they call the nits, then those nits would form into - what they used to call bugs. Well I don't know how many times - I - my head to be combed. 'Cos that - you see, those
 days - they'd make your head itch. And you could feel crawling along. Ah, that is - that's quite right. Anybody is as doing of it, or anybody like that, they'd have something white on their lap, and then - they'd come in the - on these 'ere piece of - we
ll, rag call it, then you could see them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did the girls with the livestock have to sit separately?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No. No. No. No, they weren't separated. No, you see - you understand this - some sat with dirty heads, well - and then the ones with the clean head
s - and they did catch it too, 'cos I tell you I was one of 'em. That's another thing. That be, you know - at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They examined you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see you could see them falling about. Parents didn't take enough care with children see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were some of the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 children\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  clothes dirty too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I'm afraid they weren't all clean - and in those days I'll tell you what, we had to wear pinafores over our dresses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were they white or coloured?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Coloured. Well they was - we had stuff a purpose to make pinafores with, and then that got to coloured pinafores.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So that protected your clothing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
That did. And today - children are allowed to go to school without pinafores. No aprons on. You know, little aprons purpose. Then of course the dresses get dirty don't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Before you went to school had anybody taught you the alphabet or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I don't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You learnt everything at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I did - as far as I can remember.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were the teachers particular - did you have to call the men teachers sir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I - I believe we did. Yes, we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Would you have liked to have stayed longer at school if you could have done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You were happy to leave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I - I left when I was - thirteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were you quite pleased to leave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But do you think you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Of course if I'd have stopped on for another year - of course I should have learnt more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But you had to help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I - well in those days you see you was allowed to - you could leave. You could leave that age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did your parents ever go and visit the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 There was nothing like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. Because that weren't in - that weren't in - you know, they didn't used t
o - not in those days. No. They didn't. And the only treats as far as I can remember is 1 in the summertime when we used to go up - do you know the park. Well there, we used to group there and have a treat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Would you be playing games outside?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Ye
s. In the summertime. Well then at Christmastime there'd be a Christmas tree at the school. Well we used to go to that - when we got bigger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did any sort of theatre come and do a play ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Punch and Judy show?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. Nothing like that to my know - not in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was there ever a fair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well there used to be a fair on that - used to be held down at the - Bells. I think if I remember right that's where that used to be held.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was that every year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you ask me but I really couldn't tell you. 'Cos I can't remember. I can't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But you remember there was sometimes a fair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 There was a fair, yes, it was a fair there some place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That would be just for one day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well that might have been there - per
haps a day and a night, or perhaps two nights, as far as I can remember of course - you see I was young for that, you know, to remember all that, but I remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When you got older do you remember if there was still a fair, when you were in your twenties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It stopped did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
That was all stopped because - then, you see, there used to be one down at Earls Colne in the meadow, you see. Then there used to be one at Halstead. That's where they used to go. Or - when the flower show 
was on - you see there'd be - one up there. Well that's when we lived at Hungry Hall. Where there used to be shooting parties. So we had to go and light the fire, and there used to be the butler come - and wait on the table. And sometimes they was also al
l
owed to go in the room. And you want to see what - you know, they used to bring in. And then - pheasants - was hung up in the shed overnight and ready to go - by next day. But - you won't catch them, give us a brace. You wouldn't catch a governor - give -
 give a brace.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 He would?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No. No. We might have a rabbit. 'Cos there was plenty of rabbits about those days. And then there's what they call the - the drive - no, I can't think of the name.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 The beaters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's right, the beaters. They used to have their lunch in the barn, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Who were the beaters, were they local people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
No, they was off the land - and different ones round. Perhaps there'd be - well - half a dozen. 'Cos you see they'd drive the birds while the others - t
he guns - shoot. 'Cos they had dogs on purpose for - getting the game. You see that was from - and they come different times. That don't matter if that rained, they'd come. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They'd come from quite far away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Different - different - gentlemen used to come. Well perhaps there'd be say about half a dozen guns.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Would they stay overnight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Just the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I - I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 ain\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  got nowhere to put 'em. Well you can't, I mean to say - no, they go back again, they'd come certain time in the morning and leave off - certain time in the afternoon. That's how they used to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But the poor people didn't get any of the birds?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. Tell you, they might have a rabbit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But not the birds?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. So that's as far as I can te
ll you. When I went fruit picking one day - that would happen in Colne Engaine - well the horse - fell - fell right over. You know, in the draw - they call 'em draws then. And I went and sat up - sat on the head so it wouldn't kick. And didn't the people 
look. You see, that's the best thing to do, is to go and sit on the head and then they can't kick. Yes. That's what I thought best.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You told me that most of your clothes were handed down from one child to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, that's right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember clothes being bought new?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Not always, because you - you see we couldn't afford it. No. Sometimes - see sometimes - well you see if you went to a jumble sale you could get some very good things, and things in those days was much cheaper 
than what they are today. And another thing, people don't want the cast off clothes some of 'em don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you get new clothes at any particular time of the year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Just when there was a jumble sale?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You see - oh, of course we u
sed to have some new things mind you. That is when - you see when they're worn out, you could - they couldn't be worn again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And they would be got in Halstead would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. 'Cos there was no trains running not - not in those days were there. 
There was no buses, there was no bicycles and there was - well there might have been one or two cars but - few - well - want - if you want to go shopping well you have to - you had to walk there and walk back. But I've walked there many a time. In fact I'
ve walked right the way - well we used to live at Hungry Hall, that's the - going }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 Pebmash}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
 way, walk - well then - I walked to Halstead, come all round there by Earls Colne. And - then back by the park. But still you didn't think much to it those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You were telling me about your difficulties with water?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was there any place that you could have a bath those days or didn't people have a bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, they didn't. No, they didn't. Washed, that's all. Well you see, there wasn't - there w
as no bathrooms. And no - no - coppers in the houses, not to wash in. A lot there wasn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you wash in cold water then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. Had to heat it on the stove. That's how every little - every - same as washing up. Well you had to have - well - proba
bly anybody used to keep a saucepan purpose you see for water. Well - you heat that and then use it like that. No sinks. You'd think in a farmhouse there'd be a sink wouldn't you. But there was no sinks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What did you wash your hands in then, just an enamel basin?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 A - on the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 A basin on the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Well there was - nothing else to have, you couldn't - you couldn't use that - have anything else you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you have a wash down always one special night of the week, once a week, or would it be more than that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Once a week we - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was it usually on one particular night or just when you felt like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well, probably that was - used to be the end of the week. Then of course you see you took the water upstairs,
 and washed afore you got into bed like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you had to carry it up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Would that be in a jug? Or in the basin?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh - well in - well, you ask me, well I'll say a jug.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It would be very hard to carry it in a basin?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It's interesting all the different things people had to do then which they don't have to do now isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, of course they don't, 'cos see now, here, well there }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 ain\rquote t}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  been a bathroom here not extra while. But - seven or eight, or migh
t be nine years. 'Cos you used to have to go right across that big house after every drop of water, for washing as well. You know that's hard work. Ah that was hard work in those days I can tell you. But do you see there was no wash basins upstairs, even 
in that house. Had the wash basins }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 ain\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  been in there - not 'til - and baths, one or two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 This was at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 Sewell\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 At }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 Sewell\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 , yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They just had hip baths?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. One - one or two. Then there was one round bath.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But you didn't have anything like that, it was all in the basin?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 Yes, well I tell you, you could - you could not afford the baths. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Just a minute, well then the water had to be had - heated in the copper downstairs. Every drop of hot water had to be lugged upstairs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 This was at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 Sewell\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you have to carry that then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Yes. Some of it I did. When there was two of us - but when there was two of us the - housemaid used to have to do it. When she was out that was my job. I can tell you I - I did work hard over there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Water's so heavy too isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
That is. And especially when you get a big old enamel - can, you know, these big - perhaps you haven't seen those big ones. Oh well, and they're heavy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Can you remember if you ever left any food on your plate when you were a child what your parents would say, or did you never leave it?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I don't - I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It didn't arise?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. We had to eat it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember if the food was given to you, your father first, was he served first with the food or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well mother used to serve as well. You see, that used to - then the younger ones had to - you know, that come down like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 The youngest ones were the last were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Oh we all had it at the table together mind you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You all sat down together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did your father get his the first do you remember?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I think - well I think he did have it cut - you know, have it on his plate first Yes. 'Cos when there's a half 
dozen or seven or eight to - to - cut for - you know, it make a difference. And - in those days mind you, you know these Dutch ovens? Well a Dutch oven is - there's a - oven is one side, then there's the fireplace. And - and that's what that, you had to c
ook on there or else go without.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Do you remember what funerals were like in those early years of your life, were they different from how they are today?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I can - well you see - they used to have what they call a bier. To take 'em - the coffin
s on. 'Cos that used to be drawn by men. Yes, that did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well I really - I can't - that is - no - I know, I know what you mean. 'Cos one of 'em is, we thank thee Lord for this our food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You used to say that did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I said - that was a - we used to say that at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Do you remember if there was one of your brothers or sisters that you played with rather more than the others, were you more with your sister who was nearer you in age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 We
ll I think we was all alike. You know - you know, because - there was no difference. You know, we - there weren't - one pet - one made a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 A fuss of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No, that's what I mean. No, we was all served alike.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But there was one sister quite close to you in age, about a year and nine months?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you spend more time with her than the others or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well you see, 'course we - these two - me and her, you see we went to school together, and - and because see the others, as
 they come along they had left school before we did, that's how it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So you always used to go along together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You told me about getting six strokes of the cane for being a few minutes late so being punctual at school was important wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well that's because you see I went down with a - my schoolmates. Well then we was late for school. That's how that happened. But - but that's the only - only time I can remember having a - cane like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did you give any of the money you earned to your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well not - because - I did - I did when I went to - when I went - used to do - do stone picking or - like that. Yes, I used to give - give a little, well I - 'course see I had to buy me clothes you know. And the
re weren't much to spare out of it I can tell you. And we weren't allowed to take - spend money for sweets. Well you couldn't, it's no good, you could not do it in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 It had to go to the important things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Of course it did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You found all your own clothes when you started working did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh yes. When I - you know, after I went in that - in the fields to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 How did you save it, do you remember, did you put it in the Post Office or in a little tin box?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well there wasn't enough - but afterwards, that did go in the bank - in the Post Office. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 At first it wasn't enough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh no, it wasn't enough. Yes, that was, they was hard days in that time. Yes. They were hard days. And you see we wasn't allowed to go ou
t - well another thing there weren't there - there weren't - there were a few children over the - road, but - you see, when that was - when that was wintertime, you see, we didn't - we didn't go out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Because of the dark?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was. We had to go to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In the summer you could play with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Oh yes, we was allowed to go - just outside. But not - and then of course you see - well I don't know, have you seen what they used to have for children, babies? Had like a little wagon. No -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Just two wheels?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Four wheels, no, four. Well then there was a - where they used to draw it - by a handle, you know, that used to be - like that and a - piece - this piece like that. Well they used to have that, but no rubber - no rubber wheels. You know, no tyres.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Is that what you used to take the baby out in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Ah, these other people did. What I used to be friendly with. Yes, they used to go to take the baby for - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15664903\charrsid14557479 a ride}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 , well - I used to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You used to go along with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 That was a different baby from the one that got to know you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Ah you see, 'cos - that lot - they had a very big family, that lot. Yes, that was, they were - that was a large family. Then of course they moved - to Pebmarsh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 There were a lot of large families then weren't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
I should think there was some large families. And another thing you see there was no - no - allowance for children those days, not like there is today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When you were a little girl all the family was at home weren't they, they hadn't gone off anywhere to live away or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Well you see as they - the elder ones, they start to marry you see. And then of course they had a home of their own. One used to live at Peb - yes, one used to live Pebmarsh, another
 one used to live at - Maplestead. Then of course the others you see, two of 'em, they was - went in service. Then you see the - then another one married, like that. And then - you see the others was single until - and then - then another one married. And
 two of 'em never married at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12338890\charrsid14557479 One of your sister}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 s didn't marry did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Two of 'em didn't marry. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So bit by bit they dispersed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But in the early days they were all at home when you were a small child?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well of course they was until they could - you know -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You were all quite close together really weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Yes. There weren't a lot - wasn't - wasn't a lot of difference. Well I've only told what - what's right. Nothing - another thing I shouldn't like to tell you anything what's wrong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 We've been over such a lot of things about those times haven't we?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Was there a policeman in the village at that time in Colne Engaine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 There used to be one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 There isn't now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. There isn't, of course there used to be one - live where - where - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12338890\charrsid14557479 
Markham}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  used to be a policeman, in down in - in the village.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were there any crimes, did people ever get run in for doing things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Not like there is - not - as there is today. You didn't - yes, but there weren't the stealing as what there is today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did boys steal apples then at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh that's - well that - that was only natural was it. Because I was one of 'em. Yes, I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 But all children did that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 And the policeman didn't bother about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well they didn't say anything. Well of course they'd warn you, but that was enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What about people who poached, were they ever had up, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12338890\charrsid14557479 prosecuted}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  for poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I - well see they weren't ca
ught. And see they could go about when the - the moon shine, and another thing you see, when the - when - the - well - same as - my brothers you see, when they had finished work well they didn't want to go out far after that. 'Cos they'd got - according t
h
ey was working you see they'd got a decent way to walk. And people used to walk miles in those days to work. And they used to have to work - start six o'clock. And seven o'clock in the winter. And there didn't used to be no holiday, no weeks holiday. They
 used to leave off I think at - about four or five in - for - until afterwards you understand, and that's all the hours - that's all the time they had off.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In our village the union tried to get the men not to go back on Saturday afternoons, have just the mornings, was that the same here?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, same - after a time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Were the men frightened to stop away in the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Oh that I - well - see I really can't - I couldn't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 In our village the men were very frightened to stay away when the farmer wanted them there in case they lost their jobs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
Yes. Well - you see, they - when anybody left their job and went to another place, they had to have a reference. And if that reference wasn't good enough well they wouldn't take 'em. 
And so the maids just the same, if their - if - they left one place and wanted another one, well they had a - write - then the - where they went you understand, say you employed one, well you'd have to write back to the former mistress for to see what sor
t of - what sort of - reference they give.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did they call it a character?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes. Character or reference. Yes. Well it's all the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 So when you started working at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12338890\charrsid14557479 Sewell's}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  did you have to have one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 No. 'Cos they knew you, 'cos they knew what I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Because you were from the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You caught a rabbit with a stick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Caught it with my hand. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You didn't hit it with a stick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 I think I killed it - my - with this hand, you know, at the back of the hea
d. You catch hold of them by the hind legs - and then - you know, back of the neck. And I did tell you where I went to a - to a - well it was - a show you might say where I caught a pig didn't I. Well I did. And I tried another place for a - that was a

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You caught a rabbit with a stick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Caught it with my hand. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 You didn't hit it with a stick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 
I think I killed it - my - with this hand, you know, at the back of the head. You catch hold of them by the hind legs - and then - you know, 
back of the neck. And I did tell you where I went to a - to a - well it was - a show you might say where I caught a pig didn't I. Well I did. And I tried another place for a - that was a greasy pig, but I lost it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They'd greased it's sides had they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes, all over.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 When you caught that rabbit did you skin it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Yes I did skin it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 What did you do with the skin?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Used to sell 'em then. And some of 'em used to fetch good price. Providing they wasn't tore about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Who used to come and buy them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well perhaps there'd be a - well these people used to come round you know to see if they could get rabbit skins.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did any }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12338890\charrsid14557479 gypsies}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  come round then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well there used to be some.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did they camp here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Well there used t
o be a place - where - you go along the Pebmarsh Road and down what they call Laces, that used to be the place for 'em. But there }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1267041\charrsid14557479 ain\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479  been none there lately. For a long time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14244734 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 Did they mix with the village people at all or did they keep to themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598283 LW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2438635\charrsid14557479 They kept to themselves, as far as I can remember.
\par }}